{"type": "article", "id": 30753, "title": "折叠型墙面储物架", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-08T23:00:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160808214235kBDv8FRuN63Kjxzd.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>对于那些想在小空间里放上滑板甚至是一辆单车的人来说，这个名为 Zero Gravity Rack 的折叠型墙面储物架可以助你“一臂之力”：设计师 Mark Canavarro 利用空气压缩技术让这个架子最多可以支撑起 22 千克重的物品，有效地提升了空间的利用率。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/590223522/zero-gravity-racks-the-storage-rack-everyone-needs/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 119 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215213RZaDEPJO4omic1gw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.486250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160808215213o60vZcFsXeSbQY3a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.369118\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}